{"tid":2206534,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪大律師個人照曝光！笑容燦爛盡顯專業人士感覺！","createTime":"2020-09-17T13:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T16:07:32.000Z","uid":9573,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb25bb994c58ff7ab811d5248a94192a8d9b2bd","tid":2206534,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"朱千雪（Tracy）早前正式獲聘成為大律師，投身法律界。律師樓官網更新佢嘅個人簡介，加咗千雪BB嘅個人照，佢笑容燦爛，盡顯專業人士感覺！<br />\n<br />\n朱千雪（Tracy）結婚後已漸漸淡出幕前專注學業，6月佢加入著名律師行做3個月大律師實習生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/holiday.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/67446370_720760398395651_4403263037443478782_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F67446370_720760398395651_4403263037443478782_n.jpg&h=2cbb7159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢喺8月尾完成實習，正式獲聘成為大律師，投身法律界。律師樓官網亦有佢嘅個人檔案，顯示千雪BB喺家庭及婚姻事務、土地等領域擁有豐富經驗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/holiday.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/62107746_391342884810599_6545436668416569301_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F62107746_391342884810599_6545436668416569301_n.jpg&h=b99370fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n律師樓官網有朱千雪嘅個人檔案，顯示千雪BB喺家庭及婚姻事務、土地等領域擁有豐富經驗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3og0IMh1KyqjTfCosU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3og0IMh1KyqjTfCosU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=7b6d6e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/holiday.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Screen-Shot-2020-09-17-at-5.56.16-PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2FScreen-Shot-2020-09-17-at-5.56.16-PM.jpg&h=4b014386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日律師樓官網更新咗千雪BB嘅個人檔案，upload咗一張個人照。<br />\n相中千雪BB著上套裝，造型相當有專業人士感覺！但仍保留藍灣半島三房月租2.28萬招牌燦爛笑容，180度無遮擋俯視維多利亞港兩岸景色，更可欣賞煙花海景。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/holiday.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Screen-Shot-2020-09-17-at-5.56.32-PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2FScreen-Shot-2020-09-17-at-5.56.32-PM.jpg&h=17e3ae9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱千雪仍保留招牌燦爛笑容，感覺親切。<br />\n唔知做咗大律師嘅朱千雪以後仲會唔會拍劇呢？"},{"pid":"ba05856b6347ac6ac65b36fe18cb8c8c61a4013e","tid":2206534,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:54:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce2e0d53e8a3afd8908a9af5dc9cfcc4f1abc201","tid":2206534,"uid":82359,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:54:47.000Z","msg":"但仍保留藍灣半島三房月租2.28萬招牌燦爛笑容，180度無遮擋俯視維多利亞港兩岸景色，更可欣賞煙花海景。<br />\n<br />\n唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafcedb7792fe5532e11367be972c698a9e68de4","tid":2206534,"uid":190789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ce2e0d53e8a3afd8908a9af5dc9cfcc4f1abc201","tid":2206534,"uid":82359,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:54:47.000Z","msg":"但仍保留藍灣半島三房月租2.28萬招牌燦爛笑容，180度無遮擋俯視維多利亞港兩岸景色，更可欣賞煙花海景。<br />\n<br />\n唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:57:34.000Z","msg":"真係笑撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b611f8d856a504db864d6169ee453ba9b03594f","tid":2206534,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce2e0d53e8a3afd8908a9af5dc9cfcc4f1abc201","tid":2206534,"uid":82359,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:54:47.000Z","msg":"但仍保留藍灣半島三房月租2.28萬招牌燦爛笑容，180度無遮擋俯視維多利亞港兩岸景色，更可欣賞煙花海景。<br />\n<br />\n唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:59:20.000Z","